<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[]</span> أبو وَهب الكَلاعي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>هو أبو وهب عُبَيْدُ اللهِ بن عُبَيْدِ الكَلاعي.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>روى عن مكحول.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عُبَيْد الله،<span class="c5"> وعُبَيْد:</span> مصغران.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والكَلاعي:</span> بفتح الكاف.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>